interpretation:
The Black Circle card represents the unknown and the infinite. This card symbolizes the completion of a cycle and the beginning of a new one. It suggests that the querent has reached a point of closure, but also that there is more to be discovered. The Black Circle can also indicate that the querent is seeking protection, as this symbol has been used for centuries to ward off evil.

In readings, this card invites the querent to embrace the mystery of life and to trust that everything will unfold as it should. It suggests that the querent may be feeling a sense of completion or closure, but also that there is more to be explored. The Black Circle can indicate that the querent is ready to face the unknown with courage and confidence.

Keywords associated with this card include mystery, completion, infinity, and protection. The Black Circle is a powerful symbol that encourages the querent to embrace the unknown and to trust in the journey ahead.
